{"tid":2174681,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓮塘香園圍口岸下午啟用　議員憂通關對北區設施添壓力","createTime":"2020-08-26T04:44:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T04:45:39.000Z","uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0ddc547b16c007a661fb24537ea140869e5c35e","tid":2174681,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"蓮塘/香園圍口岸開通儀式上午在口岸貨檢區域舉行，貨檢通道和相關服務設施下午4時正式啓用。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，廣東省委書記李希、港澳辦副主任張曉明、行政長官林鄭月娥等出席儀式。<br />\n<br />\n  有港商、貨運及交通業界認為，新口岸可節省時間和成本，有北區區議員就憂慮，客運日後通關後，區內設施未必能應付"},{"pid":"600e38da4054b710b99f72011396df1b00102b33","tid":2174681,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1545940_1_L_20200826123449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1545940_1_L_20200826123449.jpg&h=b7b3ed9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又輸人武肺病毒~!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}